import React from 'react'
import navBar from './NavBar'
import {BrowserRouter as Route, Router, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

export default function navApp() {
  return (
    <>
    <Router>
        <navBar/>
        <Switch>
            <Route path='/'/>
        </Switch>
    </Router>
    </>
  )
}
